27
00:02:49,026 --> 00:02:50,489
Shelby!

28
00:02:51,500 --> 00:02:53,376
- Carroll Shelby.
- What?

29
00:02:53,501 --> 00:02:55,767
This is something
you can't ignore anymore.

30
00:02:55,926 --> 00:02:58,342
I take the pills. The pills work.

31
